title.narrative: Implementation Science to Strengthen Family Health (IS4FH)

description.narrative: (USAID Global Health (GH)): &lt;!--br {mso-data-placement:same-cell;}--&gt;The overall goal of the new implementation science mechanism is to expand access to high-quality voluntary family planning and improve healthy timing and spacing of births. This new activity, which is currently under design, will support research to answer priority implementation science questions as well as technical assistance to build capacity for data analysis, evidence synthesis and adoption of evidence-based practices.
